Introduction

Zhang Yuge (simplified Chinese: 张语格; traditional Chinese: 張語格; pinyin: Zhāng Yǔgé) is a Chinese idol singer.
She is a graduated member of SNH48 (Team SII), and a former member of its sub-units SEN7ES (also known as 7SENSES) and Style-7.
Following her graduation, Tako made her solo debut on January 29, 2021 with the single '人鱼' (Renyu), which is a SNH48 song from Team X's 3rd stage album.

In 2020, Tako participated in the Chinese reality girl group survival show Idol Producer 3 (Youth With You 2020), which aired on March 12, 2020. She was eliminated in 20th episode with the rank 23rd.

[2022.10.31] - Announced departure from SEN7ES.
